## ⚠️ Priority 3: Missing Head Nurse Sidebar Entries

Add 5+ hidden pages to head-nurse sidebar (see head-nurse section above for full diff).

## ℹ️ Priority 4: Optimization Opportunities

1. **Server-side filtering for tasks/directives** — Patient detail fetches ALL tasks then client-side filters by `patient_id`. Consider adding `patient_id` parameter to the API calls when dataset grows.
2. **Polling consistency** — Dashboard polls alerts @ 15s and vitals @ 30s, but emergency only polls alerts @ 30s. Consider aligning intervals.
3. **Floorplan CSS classes** — `floorplans/page.tsx` uses `text-on-surface` and `text-on-surface-variant` CSS classes (non-Tailwind) while other pages use `text-foreground` and `text-muted-foreground`. Should standardize.

